(18, 'DwrgYkmyMHKKkajnohQk', 'The Houstonian Hotel', '111 N Post Oak Ln', 'Hotels', 'Houston', 'US', '29.7684610', '-95.4596310', '77024', 'Bunker Hill Village', 5, 'The only place i\'ll stay in Houston. Fantastic service, incredibly friendly staff, great food and the best fitness options in the entire city. The rooms are a bit small and bathrooms are not luxurious by today\'s standards, but they are more than adequate and everything else about the place more than makes up for any shortcomings in that department.', 'Why go anywhere else?', 'A Traveler'),
(19, 'Cdhh4dl8m4cJCYpVB99A', 'Best Western Plus Waterville Grand Hotel', '375 Main St', 'Hotels,Hotel', 'Waterville', 'US', '44.5705900', '-69.6401200', '4901', 'ME', 4, 'I asked for a nonsmoking room and was pleased with the fact that it didn\'t seem like other people were smoking, so that\'s good. You get a 7 breakfast credit for the restaurant which was cool, although I think I prefer traditional continental breakfasts that are buffet style. The wifi was fast, so that was good. I didn\'t use the pool/hot tub/gym BUT it looked clean and ready to use. The staff was very friendly and helpful.', 'Better than I expected', 'Danielle'),
