(61, 'b4LVCT779iYiWZDZlmUS', 'Big Mountain Lodge', '6390 Us Highway 93 S', 'Hotels', 'Whitefish', 'US', '48.3911210', '-114.3358380', '59937', 'MT', 5, 'Very clean! Decent breakfast. Pleasant staff. Big thirsty towels in bathroom, and even extra towels. Comfy beds. Very quiet. Convenient to Glacier NP. A little hard to find-behind Pizza Hut and Army Surplus Store. Would absolute stay here again!', 'Pleasant experience', 'Karen'),
(62, 'p6JHmyniToyLHxV2Ezy8', 'Holiday Inn Express Atlanta Ne - I-85 Clairmont', '2920 Clairmont Rd', 'Hotels & Motels,Family-Friendly Hotels,Tourist Hotels,Weekend Getaway Hotels,Resorts,Spa Resorts,Beach Hotels,Budget Hotels,Lodging,Business Hotels', 'Atlanta', 'US', '33.8432130', '-84.3146670', '30329', 'Briarcliff', 0, 'Mid-range hotel chain with plenty of amenities for business travelers, including free in-room Wi-Fi and a 24-hour business center. In ShortCreated with business travelers in mind, Wingate Inn opened its first location in 1996. The moderately priced hotel offers perks like free wireless and high-speed Internet connections, a 24-hour business center, complimentary continental breakfast, fitness facilities and a whirlpool. Other in-room amenities include coffeemaker, iron and safe separate work area with a large desk two-line speakerphone with conference call and voice mail capabilities. For down time, there are on-demand movies and a lounge chair with ottoman.', '', 'Contributor'),
(63, 'wGdIiDmBtTYBo00DyAbR', 'Springhill Suites Columbia', '7055 Minstrel Way', 'Family-Friendly Hotels,Budget Hotels,Hotels & Motels,Business Hotels,Hotel,Tourist Hotels', 'Columbia', 'US', '39.1761280', '-76.8472570', '21046', 'MD', 5, 'We love to stay at a Marriott whenever we can. I had business in the area and needed a nice clean, safe location close to the main highway. This place did not disappoint! Easy to access, very friendly staff, clean rooms and even cleaner bathroom! Loved the toilet and shower were separate with a sink in both rooms. Mini fridge... More', 'Great, as usually - only 1 minor detail', 'SMF2_On-The-Go'),
(64, 'v5aynQvcCO6DQcRTcYFK', 'Sportsmen Motel', '2909 E Highway 101', 'Hotels,Lodging,Motels', 'Port Angeles', 'US', '48.1048500', '-123.3740600', '98362', 'Fairholm', 5, 'My parents came to visit, and we headed to Olympic National Park. We called to reserve a room at the Sportsmen Motel. I am always a little wary of strip-mall type motels, because, in my experience, they usually seem to be seedy/druggy/scary. So, when we got there, we asked to see a room first. I was pleasantly surprised. We stayed the night, and not only was the staff (a mother and daughter) very friendly and accommodating, giving restaurant recommendations (try Blue Flame BBQ a few bu...view moreildings away...oh.my.god.), but the room was cleaner than my house (really clean), the second bed had its own locking bedroom, and there was a full kitchen, with a big fridge, pots and pans, plates, coffee and coffee maker, etc. It was 90, including tax, and I was very impressed. This place rocks!view less', 'My parents came to visit, and ...', 'katiegigharbor'),
(65, 'vGrAOsyET3XAEWwx8erA', 'North Country Inn B & B', '2541 Main St', 'Bed & Breakfasts,Hotels & Motels,Lodging,Bed & Breakfast & Inns,Motels,B&bs / Inns', 'Rangeley', 'US', '44.9654100', '-70.6431740', '4970', 'Lang Twp', 5, 'We were fortunate to have selected the NCI BB for our three day stay in Rangeley while attending the various functions related to a family wedding up the road at Quimby Pond. While we had been in the area in the past (staying with family) we can NOT say enough about the very clean Inn the delicious breakfasts, prepared... More', 'Very spectacular convenient location.', 'ed w'),
