(140, 'wNTQgYIBa9zpHLy6ViZ7', 'Bent Elbow', '1114 Blair St', 'Hotels & Motels', 'Silverton', 'US', '37.8104430', '-107.6641630', '81433', 'CO', 1, 'Made a reservation over the phone for the fourth of July ten months in advance. Used a cc to confirm. Called a couple weeks later to confirm once again and was assured everything was fine. Received a call 7 months in advance saying our reservations were cancelled, citing that a fill in had messed up. When pressed, the manager was... More', 'Awful customer service', 'zealot42'),
