(142, 'WSDbVRsHysPIxF1QbKTr', 'La Quinta Inn and Suites Sunrise', '13600 N W 2nd St', 'Hotels', 'Fort Lauderdale', 'US', '26.1239810', '-80.3313150', '33325', 'Plantation', 2, 'The hotel was partially renovated, but the room wad not clean. There were ants everywhere, on the desk, on the walls, on the night tables... The bed mattress was blood stained. We had reserved for four nights, but checked out the first morning.', 'Lack of cleanliness.', 'Gary'),
