(272, 'T4NkjadDUtwZPkLqlP3l', 'Holiday Inn Rutland-killington Area', '476 Holiday Dr', 'Hotels & Motels,Family-Friendly Hotels,Tourist Hotels,Weekend Getaway Hotels,Luxury Hotels,Resorts,Beach Hotels,Budget Hotels,Conventions,Lodging,Business Hotels,Conference & Convention Centers', 'Rutland', 'US', '43.5935900', '-72.9623710', '05701-4925', 'VT', 0, 'For more than 50 years, this hotel\'s familiar green sign has signaled budget-friendly lodging for families and business travelers. In ShortSince its 1952 debut in Memphis, Tenn., Holiday Inn has become one of the most recognized hotel brands in the world. Kids rule here: Children age 19 and younger stay for free when sharing a parent\'s room and as many as four children per family (age 12 or younger) eat for free at hotel restaurants. Other amenities include 24-hour business services, an in-room coffeemaker, iron, hair dryer, room service, a swimming pool and a fitness center.', '', 'Contributor'),
