(445, '7thFgecHW0GGrQxNjiNl', 'Days Inn Berea Ky', '1029 Cooper Dr', 'Hotels & Motels', 'Berea', 'US', '37.6168000', '-84.3456010', '40403', 'KY', 0, 'Value-conscious hotel with the sunburst sign provides basic amenities to ensure travelers a comfortable stay. In ShortThis nationwide chain promises value-added amenities to its guests. King and two-queen guest rooms offer clock radios, hair dryers, shampoo, televisions with HBO or Showtime and complimentary copies of USA Today. The property is inspected three times a year for quality by an independent quality assurance team and assigned a Sunburst rating, so travelers can rest assured that their accommodations are clean and comfortable.', '', 'Contributor'),
