(463, 'neYtNUjLBv8FRb1Gnydd', 'Cougar Crest Lodge', '8917 W Hawk Ridge Rd', 'Hotels,Lodging,Resorts,Bed & Breakfast & Inns', 'Coeur D Alene', 'US', '47.6641400', '-116.9027300', '83814', 'ID', 5, 'The Cougar Crest was on the tail end of our honeymoon, and by the time we pulled up to the front gate, we\'d had a harrowing skydiving experience and had been on the road for hours. It was exactly the relaxing stay we hoped for! First off, pulling up to the entrance is like sidling up to an exclusive ski... More', 'Decadent, relaxing, personal, perfect!!!', 'erinpressonladd'),
(464, 'ccS0ZLxZ3eFIo5pnokkQ', 'Springhill Suites By Marriott Sarasota Bradenton', '1020 University Pkwy', 'Hotels', 'Sarasota', 'US', '27.3818320', '-82.5497410', '34234', 'FL', 4, 'The best thing for me, besides the reasonable price (107 for Florida residents, plus the usual additional taxes and fees of course), was the jacuzzi/pool area. For once a hotel jacuzzi had super powerful muscle ache relieving jets and hot enough temp to do some good, and the spacious pool is nestled beneath some beautiful old oak trees, that are... More', 'For a good price and lots for the money at an airport hotel, this is the place!', 'anniemax'),
