(470, '6rikLxS18MYr5pLi7sjB', 'Hampton Inn Jackson Hole', '350 S Highway 89', 'Hotels & Motels,Family-Friendly Hotels,Tourist Hotels,Business Hotels,Budget Hotels', 'Jackson', 'US', '43.4843840', '-110.7622660', '83001', 'Jackson Hole', 0, 'Value-conscious hotel with the sunburst sign provides basic amenities to ensure travelers a comfortable stay. In ShortThis nationwide chain promises value-added amenities to its guests. King and two-queen guest rooms offer clock radios, hair dryers, shampoo, televisions with HBO or Showtime and complimentary copies of USA Today. The property is inspected three times a year for quality by an independent quality assurance team and assigned a Sunburst rating, so travelers can rest assured that their accommodations are clean and comfortable.', '', 'Contributor'),
