(744, 'JUMjpQj4UPii0whA21T7', 'Milliken Creek Inn', '1815 Silverado Trl', 'Hotels,Bed & Breakfasts,Hotels & Motels', 'Napa', 'US', '38.3150250', '-122.2761520', '94558', 'CA', 0, 'Sophisticated blend of Europe and Asia, bedroom and spa. The SceneThis hotel\'s twelve romantic rooms lie on the banks of the meandering Napa River. The setting is peaceful and elegant, the hospitality phenomenal. Gourmet breakfasts are packed in picnic baskets for guests to enjoy on wine country jaunts, back at the hotel\'s waterfall terrace, or, an even more popular option, in their soft down-covered beds.The DetailsUnlike many of its wine country neighbors with their frilly Victorian lace and overpowering floral wallpaper, this elegant inn takes the clean, soothing ambiance of its spa into the bedroom. Not all rooms are the same, but all are sophisticated, and appointed with fireplaces, L\'Occitane bath salts and fine Frette linens. In luxury rooms the white, khaki, lemon, and olive tones join palm fronds, gauze canopies, and Balinese fans to create a colonial Indochine flavor. In premium suites, guests can enjoy their own private spa with hydrotherapy bathtubs and a private riverfront terrace.', '', 'Contributor'),
