(779, '6cNTkzRy1RKOW00YRjQL', 'Helios Resort', '280 E Mel Ave', 'Resorts,Hotels,Lodging,Motels', 'Palm Springs', 'US', '33.8407550', '-116.5446800', '92262', 'Palm Springs Municipal Airpo', 3, 'Have been staying at this resort for so many years, and current management knows how to pamper the guests with breakfast buffet and poolside misting sprays for super hot days. Jaccuzzi is large and always at the right temperature. Pool is refreshing and music plays softly throughout the afternoons. There is a play-area were guests can explore their BDSM side, but the area has become run down and could use some repair of suspension posts and spanking tables. Easy stroll to center of town, and nearby Riveria Hotel is a retro-dream.', 'Great LIttle Hideaway', 'CactusJohn'),
