(838, 'X6GspD11YbHoXq1i5SKq', 'Royal Dutch Inn', 'Captains Bay Rd', 'Hotels,Lodging', 'Dutch Harbor', 'US', '53.8547970', '-166.5590400', '99692', 'AK', 4, 'The Royal Dutch Inn is located between a beautiful mountain slope and the Captains Bay Harbor where the fishing boats and larger transport ships ply the waters. The Bering Sea is only a few miles away where the Deadliest Catch Discovery Channel is filmed. My favorite thing about the RDI is the great restaurant next door. The Galley has great... More', 'Amazing views', 'Ramona T'),
